## Critical Issues (Must Fix)

### 1. Missing Skip Navigation Link
- **Severity:** Critical
- **WCAG Criterion:** 2.4.1 Bypass Blocks (Level A)
- **Location:** Beginning of `<body>`
- **Issue:** No skip link provided to allow keyboard users to bypass repetitive navigation
- **Impact:** Keyboard users must tab through all navigation links on every page
- **Fix:**
  ```html
  <!-- Add as first element inside <body> -->
  <a href="#showcase" class="sh-skip-link">Skip to main content</a>
  ```
  ```css
  .sh-skip-link {
      position: absolute;
      top: -100%;
      left: 50%;
      transform: translateX(-50%);
      background: var(--sh-primary);
      color: white;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: var(--sh-radius-md);
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      z-index: 9999;
  }
  .sh-skip-link:focus {
      top: 1rem;
  }
  ```
